    General Stores in Trombay, Mumbai

    (307 Ratings & Reviews) 4.1 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Trombay, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. In marketing terminology, a kirana shop is a form of traditional retail catering to the needs of citizens. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Trombay, Mumbai.
